    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite all 7 assessed credibility factors falling below required levels and 6 factors flagged as unassessed epistemic gaps, the submission is conditionally accepted pending a formal remediation plan addressing model form uncertainty, use error controls, and independent code verification. The Monte Carlo UQ campaign, while internally documented with sensitivity indices, provides sufficient uncertainty quantification evidence at the narrative level to support conditional acceptance at MRL 5. Structured sensitivity analysis linkage will be required in the remediation submission.",
